Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Mi gebɛed ɣef leɛṭeṛ-nni, a d-yenna : Lemziya n wezgen, d igellil ; yețnerni mkul yiwen seg inebgawen yesseṛɣay-is ad iɛeddin ccetwa.
