M'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, kunwi mazal teṭṭfem di ccṛeɛ deg wayen ara s-d-ssukksen, ma d igellil ( ad wten s ujelkaḍ ), neɣ m'ulac wid iḥekkmen ɣef weqcic-agi, ilaq ad yili d win iḥekkmen ɣef weqcic n wat Isṛail.
