Lɛulama n ccariɛa d imeqqranen n wegdud nnan : D irgazen-agi i gesɣaṛen iman-nsen ur d-teqbil ara ccariɛa n Musa akk-d wid iḍaɛen, ur d-yețțawi ara lfayda si tejmaɛt n temdint.
Akken i yi-d-tenna ccariɛa, ar ass-a aya i deg ara ternuḍ yid-i, eɛni ur nezmir ara a kem-rreɣ iman-iw ?
