Mi d-yewweḍ ṛebɛa uɛebbuḍ-nni, acḥal tewwet i gcerreg di tlemmast n Lǧameɛ iqedsen ; msefhamen ad kksen yiwen seg-sen aman ḥussen si tama-s.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tbuciḍant i ɣef yeṭṭaxeṛ i webrid n Ṛebbi, yesɛan azal akteṛ n ṛebɛa meyya uɛecrin n wezṛu.
Atan wamek i yi-d-iweḥḥa Sidi Ṛebbi : Ɛuṣeɣ aṭas-agi seg ul-iw, d ayen i d-yusan seg wass amezwaru armi d ɣuṛ-i. Lewḥukkam ikcem-iyi am akken ilaq, lmut n wass amezwaru i deg ilaq ad steɛfuɣ.
tella dinna lḥila n idrimen d lebḥuṛ akk-d usenduq n wat Isṛail, mkul a sen-yefk ayen i gṛuccen s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat-nsen, imiren m'ara bɣun ad ṛuḥen.
