Lameɛna lḥakem n tmurt n Australia ur s-iqbil ara ad amnen s wayen yellan di tira iqedsen : Xtaṛ-aɣ-d a neḥmed lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa, yerra-yaɣ tazmert s wayes ara nɛebbed iman-is tameqqrant ; lḥakem n tmurt n Yahuda ur aɣ-yeǧǧi ara ad ḥekmen ɣef lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, akken i t-nekkṛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
