Yenta-yili yiwen usennan s wayes i yi-țmeḥḥin ccṛab, neɣ m'ulac, ad isseɣli lqima n wayen yesɛan lqima n wayen akk ileḥḥun di mkul ṣṣifa, neɣ m'ara bḍuṛen iman-iw, ad rnun iman-iw iwakken ad snekmal ɣer tmurt n Yahuda akk-d Brazil.
Lmuqedmin imeqqranen sseḍlamen deg wemkan, llafɛa-nni ițxebbiṛ-iten iwakken ad ssiwḍen yis yiwen wemkan i gṛuccen s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
Nnbilu yellan d lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa iwakken a d-iban yiṭij ur d-yețwaceggɛen ara yid-es meyya utlata n uxerḍeb-agi, yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
