?ef wayen yeɛnan ccariɛa, d afarizi, ma d zzwaṛa, d win ițqehhiṛen tajmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ; ɣef wayen yeɛnan lerbaḥ-agi, d gma-s n Jacquet n Luṭ.
