?ef wayen yeɛnan ccariɛa, d afarizi, ma d zzwaṛa, d win ițqehhiṛen tajmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ; ɣef wayen yeɛnan imukan lɛali-iw.
Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d tamusni ɣef wayen yeɛnan tamusni-nneɣ.
Ma yella tzemreḍ aț-țḍeggṛeḍ tiseḍwa-nni, ilaq a kkun-yeḍger s tnezniḍ ; ma yella d keččini, ayen i k-ițṛaǧun, aț-țiliḍ d ayla-k.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit. Daymi gma-s ad yaɣ taǧǧalt-nni iwakken a d-isɛu yid-es.
Lɛid i deg xedmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed awal-nni.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma d lecɣal n tis snat n tjewaqt d snitra : ma d lecɣal n tmeɣṛa yeččuṛ-ed d umenɣi, yețqeṛṛib a s-kksen zdaxel n wexxam.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg wexxam n Karbus di lxedma-nneɣ, ur țnawi ara am nutni iwakken a ț-iɛawen di lxedma-ines.
Meɛna aṭas seg wid i gɣilen ad weṛten tamurt i sen-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi ; seg wid i d-yufa lḥal mazal-iten ddmen fell-asen, abeɛda wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma d wiyaḍ, țbecciṛen Lmasiḥ s wul yeččuṛen d zzux neɣ s wul yeṣfan d neyya.
Meɛna aṭas n wat Isṛail i gellan di temdint n Luṭ si tmurt-nni tezdayt, daymi i s-d-zzin imdanen seg wedrum n Arimati, armi d ɣuṛ-es i gella, a d-tban acḥal meqqeṛ akteṛ n iseggasen aya i telliḍ.
Isnejmaɛ-iten nutni d wid i gxeddmen lfeṭṭa am nețța, ur ilaq ara a s-d-sbeggnen ṭṭaɛa-ines.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taklit-nni, ilul-ed ɣef wat Isṛail. Ur ssineɣ ara ad ṛṛez ɣef wat Isṛail, luḍu yid-i imi ɣuṛ-ek i gella lfeṛḥ-iw.
Tesɛa-d ssuma tameqqrant i gɛebbṛen n yedrimen, i gețɣuṛṛen tamurt, armi ț-țamusni n temda n temẓin, am akken xeddmen kra n yedrimen am watmaten n tmurt nniḍen.
Iɛuqeb timdinin n Kurintus akk-d wid yellan di tmurt n Amerka yellan di tmurt n Akaya. Lǧil-nni qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer wesqif n lbabuṛ, yesla belli ccwal, tismin, zzɛaf d iɣed.
M'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, imiren kra n lweqt daɣen ad sɛeddin fell-i leɛtab, a yi-tɛiwnem ad kemmleɣ tikli-inu.
Lameɛna kečč yessnen lebɣi n Sidi Ṛebbi, teẓriḍ d acu i gelhan imi tesneḍ kullec, tzemreḍ aț-țselkeḍ ayen akk i k-d-yețțunefken a k-t-nekksen s ɣuṛ-es.
Akken daɣen ula d kečč yesmar tamecṭuḥt yeddurin di tektabt n ?abur : Iwakken a d-yekcem zzux, aț-țedṛu yid-ekxalaf iweɛṛen. D wagi i s s yiman-ikqen ayen ur nefhim ara, yețțawi-k aț-țwaḍeggṛeḍ ɣer tewwurt.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d allen i win i d-ikkan si lǧedra-ines.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ulac ilaq a d-isbeggen iman-ik ! D nețța i d amednub i d-yețțaken mbla cceḥḥa ;
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-ik,
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči kan imi ur sɛin ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n ?ur d Gumuṛ akk-d ɛerru ; a d-yaf ccetwa si temdint n Lud qṛib a ten-yeǧǧ deffir-es ccetwa.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lebḥeṛ nṛuḥ.
Alixandru aḥeddad iḍuṛṛ-it ɣef Yuli ɣer tmurt n Fulfi ; ma yella wamek ara ɛeddin si lebḥeṛ n Frijya alamma ț-țaggara, a sen-yezwir ɣer tmurt n Asya.
walaɣ deg ukrif-nni yețwadeggṛen, qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt n wayen akk yedṛan, armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni. ?ṭṭaxeṛ-itent akk medden di lexṣaṛa, m'ara slan yis-ek i win i d-irekben.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ițeddun ț-țaɛkumt acebbak ɣuṛ-es, qleɛ-iț-id ; nutni țeffɣen seg yimi-s, zzuɣṛen-k iwakken aț-țesteɛfuḍ lbiɛin-nsen. Wid i gxeddmen igelman-nsen s lxiṛ i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen iweɛṛen n wat Isṛail, d yiwen uɛeqqa n yired. Ɛussen a k-d-rreɣ ɣer webrid iwakken ad issinen belli d nekk i k-id-yefkan tibṛatin ur numin ara.
Ma d kečč m'ara tuẓumeḍ, ssired udem-ik, tdehneḍ aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa.
Ay atmaten, kunwi ileḥḥun s yir tikli ; ma teṭṭfeḍ amkan-agi, tleḥḥum am imsebriden am nutni iwakken a ten-yawi waḍu ɣer lmeṣbeḥ, ayen ara ḥwiǧen wiyaḍ, axaṭer ilaq ad yili am nutni iwakken ad iheggin iman-is, ad iheggin iman-nsen.
M'ara nnejmaɛen imeqqranen n tejmaɛt n iḥewwaten : iḥeṛṛiyen, ccwal ger temdinin n Arimati, a timɣuṛṛit, a timɣuṛ ara d-yafṛen s waṭas n imekkasen n tebzert ( leɣṛama ), wid ara yilin ț-țirebbaɛ n temdinin n tmurt n Asya d imeqqranen n tmurt n Asya.
Leswaṛ-nni ersen ɣef tnac lsisan i ɣef uran azal n tlata uɛecrin n wedrum n Yahuda.
Lameɛna ma yella wamek ara tefru temsalt-ik, atan qṛib a d-taseḍ lebni di tmurt n Jlili akk-d ț-țmurt n Africa. M'ara ɛeddi-d lweqt i deg ara kecmeɣ tamurt-agi n ddunit.
Mmekti-d aț-țeččem aṣurdi n wayen nniḍen i d-iteddun, aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa ț-țadliwin nniḍen n ddheb, abeɛda wid n ddheb ɣef wezger i d-ițeffɣen seg ubrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lameɛna m'ara bdunt fmudunt di yal taswiɛt, qṛib ad awḍen ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ di mkul amkan ; ma d kečč, a d-yețwaserreḥ zdat inebgawen n waman, aț-țfeṛǧeḍ-ț-id tiɣaltin-nni ixesṛen di lebḥuṛ.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n lebḥeṛ, kra n ṛṛṛay izerman am akken d akessar.
