Tesɛa-d yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef temdint n Armenia. Ger widak-nni i d-yeddan d lḥakem nniḍen, yiwen si terbaɛt n tegzirt-nni ;
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas yiwen umeslay-nni, ițheggi-yaɣ-d iman-is iwakken a d-issufeɣ si tmura n Armenya akk-d Azerbaijan.
