S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass ɣef tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddigen, tqeɛɛed ; ma d kra deg-sen ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen n diri.
Axiṛ-iyi wayen i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi ad ifak, timeslayin ur nețwassen ara ad ḥebsent, tamusni aț-țefnu, ma d leḥmala n tideț werǧin aț-țfak ;
yeqqim-aɣ-ed kan a neṛǧu s lxuf ameqqran lḥisab i d-ițeddun ț-țmes iṛeqqen ara yeččen wid iɛuṣan Ṛebbi.
Meɛna ɣas akken llan wid yețmeslayen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ma yella terram-t deg uḥewt-ik, ula d kunwi aț-țeffɣen seg wedrar-nni yexlan s yiman-nwen.
Ula d gma-k a tamdint n Siyun, d ayen i gesderɣeḍ am tesbeddeḍ lebni. Deg umkan-ik tețțuleqm di ccariɛa, ma d kečč i gesbedd lqedd-is ayen yelhan, d ass i deg tesbedd lqedd-is uqbel ad yezni.
Aɛebbed-agi i wen-d-yețțaken tudert, azeggaɣ akk-d leḥrir aṛqaq ;
Ɣas akken ṛṛusul nnan asen imeslayen-agi, s lḥif ameqqran i ḥebsen lɣaci-nni :
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, lameɛna xeddmen aṭas n wid yețțaɣen awal !
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-asen, ur sɛiɣ ara tazmert a s-rreɣ iman-iw, ad rnun iman-iw ad rnun yid-i, ad rnun zzin-iyi am akken d aɛeṛqen.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset iman-nwen am tiyritin ; ur nezmir ara a nexdem tameɣṛa akk-d imukan yexlan i deg tecɛelli.
